-- MOVES-Co-operative Bank appoints Derek Weir as non-executive director 
-- 
-- Fri Jul 25, 2014 01:29PM EDT
-- None



July 25 (Reuters) - UK-based Co-operative Bank said it appointed Derek Weir as an independent non-executive director.

Over his 25 years of experience in the financial services industry, Weir has held a range of senior positions, including ones at Barclays Bank Plc <BARC.L> and Royal Bank of Scotland Plc <RBS.L>, the bank said.